made 2020/07/14 approx per

https://www.cookingclassy.com/beef-tomato-macaroni-soup/

2.31 lb 90% ground beef, did drain
some vegetable oil for sauteing veggies
1 giant onion, sauteed
4 normal carrots, sauteed
2 quarts beef broth
2x16 oz can tomato sauce
4x14.5 oz can petite diced tomatoes, not drained
1/4 cup worcestershire sauce
thyme
1 lb macaroni
2x15.25 oz cans corn, drained, added when macaroni was mostly done
8 oz package cream cheese, microwave softened and mixed in pretty much last thing
misc garlic, salt, pepper
